"<guimenuitem>Collapse All Categories</guimenuitem>: Collapses the tree to "
"show only top level modules and categories."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Sažmi sve kategorije</guimenuitem>: sažima stablo tako da se "
"vide samo moduli na vrhu i kategorije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Expand All Categories</guimenuitem>: Expands the tree to show "
"modules."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Raširi sve kategorije</guimenuitem>: širi stablo tako da se "
"vide svi moduli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Clear Search</guimenuitem>: This will clear any filter you have "
"applied on the module listing via the search box"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Očisti pretragu</guimenuitem>: čisti filter koji ste možda "
